Package com.project.moviebooking.exception

package com.project.moviebooking.exception
The "exception" package contains custom exception classes used within the movie booking application.

Exception classes in this package represent specific error conditions, faults, or exceptional scenarios that may occur during the execution of the movie booking system. These custom exceptions encapsulate detailed error information and are thrown to handle exceptional cases and provide meaningful error messages to users or client applications.

Organizing exception classes in this package helps centralize and manage custom exception handling, enabling precise error handling and effective communication of error conditions within the application.
